summary: An ordinance accepting a deed from the Milwaukee Land Company, a corporation, organized and existing under and by virtue of the laws of the State of Iowa, dated April 29, 1912, to a certain tract, piece or parcel of land in the Southwest quarter of Section 34, Township 23 North, Range 8 East, W.M., and providing for the payment therefor by a warrant drawn on the Cedar River Water Shed Condemnation Fund.
